<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>php artisan make:migration add_delete_at_to_post_table <span class="nt">--table</span><span class="o">=</span>Posts
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>dans le fichier cr√©er, on met √† jour les schemas en se servant de la <a href="https://laravel.com/docs/9.x/eloquent#querying-soft-deleted-models">documentation</a></p>
<div class="language-php highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">use</span> <span class="nc">Illuminate\Database\Schema\Blueprint</span><span class="p">;</span>
