<h2 id="supprimer-d√©finitivement">supprimer d√©finitivement</h2>

<p>:warning: <strong>Warning:</strong> Le post est supprim√© d√©finitivement.</p>

<div class="language-php highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$post</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nc">Post</span><span class="o">:</span><span class="nf">find</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">);</span>

